Package: TextMiningCrisis
Type: Package
Title: Natural Language Processing (NPL) on IMF reports
Version: 2.0.0
Date: 2020-01-23
Author: Betin Manuel, Umberto Collodel
Maintainer: <manubetin@gmail.com>
Description: Perform a text analysis using a lexicon of economic crisis on a corpus of IMF documents. Toolbox for the construction and extension of the Complex Crises Database (CCD) : https://doi.org/10.7910/DVN/CN0PR9
